        }
      ],
      "Speed": 0.0,
      "FontSize": 0,
      "WhenFinishCloseWindow": 0,
      "RequirePlayEffect": 0,
      "EffectReferenceIdx": 0,
      "RequirePlaySound": 0,
      "SoundReferenceIdx": 0,
      "TargetValueScale": 0.0
    },
    {
      "TalkCharacters": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297
        }
      ],
      "WindowDisplayName": "Mizuki",
      "Body": "There were times you worked all the way until morning and just went straight to school, right?",
      "TalkTention": 0,
      "LipSync": 1,
      "MotionChangeFrom": 1,
      "Motions": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297,
          "MotionName": "w-normal04-nod",
          "FacialName": "face_worry_01",
          "TimingSyncValue": 0.0
        }
      ],
      "Voices": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297,
          "VoiceId": "voice_ev_night_25_05_25_20",
          "Volume": 1.0
        }
      ],
      "Speed": 0.0,
      "FontSize": 0,
      "WhenFinishCloseWindow": 0,
      "RequirePlayEffect": 0,
      "EffectReferenceIdx": 0,
      "RequirePlaySound": 0,
      "SoundReferenceIdx": 0,
      "TargetValueScale": 0.0
    },
    {
      "TalkCharacters": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 272
        }
      ],
      "WindowDisplayName": "Mizuki's Sister",
      "Body": "'There totally were! My skin was a mess, I honestly wonder how I managed to pull it off~.'",
      "TalkTention": 0,
      "LipSync": 1,
      "MotionChangeFrom": 1,
      "Motions": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 272,
          "MotionName": "s-common-nod01",
          "FacialName": "face_closeeye_03",
          "TimingSyncValue": 0.0
        }
      ],
      "Voices": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 272,
          "VoiceId": "voice_ev_night_25_05_26_140",
          "Volume": 1.0
        }
      ],
      "Speed": 0.0,
      "FontSize": 0,
      "WhenFinishCloseWindow": 0,
      "RequirePlayEffect": 0,
      "EffectReferenceIdx": 0,
      "RequirePlaySound": 0,
      "SoundReferenceIdx": 0,
      "TargetValueScale": 0.0
    },
    {
      "TalkCharacters": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297
        }
      ],
      "WindowDisplayName": "Mizuki",
      "Body": "It made me worried just watching you. I thought you were going to collapse one day.",
      "TalkTention": 0,
      "LipSync": 1,
      "MotionChangeFrom": 1,
      "Motions": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297,
          "MotionName": "w-normal08-nod",
          "FacialName": "face_trouble_02",
          "TimingSyncValue": 0.0
        }
      ],
      "Voices": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297,
          "VoiceId": "voice_ev_night_25_05_27_20",
          "Volume": 1.0
        }
      ],
      "Speed": 0.0,
      "FontSize": 0,
      "WhenFinishCloseWindow": 0,
      "RequirePlayEffect": 0,
      "EffectReferenceIdx": 0,
      "RequirePlaySound": 0,
      "SoundReferenceIdx": 0,
      "TargetValueScale": 0.0
    },
    {
      "TalkCharacters": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297
        }
      ],
      "WindowDisplayName": "Mizuki",
      "Body": "(...I guess designing and actually making things yourself really is tough.)",
      "TalkTention": 0,
      "LipSync": 2,
      "MotionChangeFrom": 1,
      "Motions": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297,
          "MotionName": "w-normal08-sad",
          "FacialName": "face_sad_01",
          "TimingSyncValue": 0.0
        }
      ],
      "Voices": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297,
          "VoiceId": "voice_ev_night_25_05_28_20",
          "Volume": 1.0
        }
      ],
      "Speed": 0.0,
      "FontSize": 0,
      "WhenFinishCloseWindow": 0,
      "RequirePlayEffect": 0,
      "EffectReferenceIdx": 0,
      "RequirePlaySound": 0,
      "SoundReferenceIdx": 0,
      "TargetValueScale": 0.0
    },
    {
      "TalkCharacters": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297
        }
      ],
      "WindowDisplayName": "Mizuki",
      "Body": "(I've altered clothes... and made costumes when Rui asked me to, but I didn't make those from absolute scratch, either.)",
      "TalkTention": 0,
      "LipSync": 2,
      "MotionChangeFrom": 1,
      "Motions": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297,
          "MotionName": "w-normal15-tilthead",
          "FacialName": "face_smallmouth_01",
          "TimingSyncValue": 0.0
        }
      ],
      "Voices": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297,
          "VoiceId": "voice_ev_night_25_05_29_20",
          "Volume": 1.0
        }
      ],
      "Speed": 0.0,
      "FontSize": 0,
      "WhenFinishCloseWindow": 0,
      "RequirePlayEffect": 0,
      "EffectReferenceIdx": 0,
      "RequirePlaySound": 0,
      "SoundReferenceIdx": 0,
      "TargetValueScale": 0.0
    },
    {
      "TalkCharacters": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 272
        }
      ],
      "WindowDisplayName": "Mizuki's Sister",
      "Body": "'Well, it's all important for studying fashion. Thanks to that hardship, I'm somehow able to push through how busy I am now, though.'",
      "TalkTention": 0,
      "LipSync": 1,
      "MotionChangeFrom": 1,
      "Motions": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 272,
          "MotionName": "s-common-nod01",
          "FacialName": "face_smile_06",
          "TimingSyncValue": 0.0
        }
      ],
      "Voices": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 272,
          "VoiceId": "voice_ev_night_25_05_30_140",
          "Volume": 1.0
        }
      ],
      "Speed": 0.0,
      "FontSize": 0,
      "WhenFinishCloseWindow": 0,
      "RequirePlayEffect": 0,
      "EffectReferenceIdx": 0,
      "RequirePlaySound": 0,
      "SoundReferenceIdx": 0,
      "TargetValueScale": 0.0
    },
    {
      "TalkCharacters": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297
        }
      ],
      "WindowDisplayName": "Mizuki",
      "Body": "I see...",
      "TalkTention": 0,
      "LipSync": 1,
      "MotionChangeFrom": 1,
      "Motions": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297,
          "MotionName": "w-normal15-nod",
          "FacialName": "face_sad_01",
          "TimingSyncValue": 0.0
        }
      ],
      "Voices": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297,
          "VoiceId": "voice_ev_night_25_05_31_20",
          "Volume": 1.0
        }
      ],
      "Speed": 0.0,
      "FontSize": 0,
      "WhenFinishCloseWindow": 0,
      "RequirePlayEffect": 0,
      "EffectReferenceIdx": 0,
      "RequirePlaySound": 0,
      "SoundReferenceIdx": 0,
      "TargetValueScale": 0.0
    },
    {
      "TalkCharacters": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297
        }
      ],
      "WindowDisplayName": "Mizuki",
      "Body": "Well, I'm used to pulling all-nighters for my usual work, so I think I'll be fine on that front, but...",
      "TalkTention": 0,
      "LipSync": 1,
      "MotionChangeFrom": 1,
      "Motions": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297,
          "MotionName": "w-happy09-tilthead",
          "FacialName": "face_smile_06",
          "TimingSyncValue": 0.0
        }
      ],
      "Voices": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297,
          "VoiceId": "voice_ev_night_25_05_32_20",
          "Volume": 1.0
        }
      ],
      "Speed": 0.0,
      "FontSize": 0,
      "WhenFinishCloseWindow": 0,
      "RequirePlayEffect": 0,
      "EffectReferenceIdx": 0,
      "RequirePlaySound": 0,
      "SoundReferenceIdx": 0,
      "TargetValueScale": 0.0
    },
    {
      "TalkCharacters": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297
        }
      ],
      "WindowDisplayName": "Mizuki",
      "Body": "Ah, but—",
      "TalkTention": 0,
      "LipSync": 1,
      "MotionChangeFrom": 1,
      "Motions": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297,
          "MotionName": "w-normal03-trouble",
          "FacialName": "face_smallmouth_01",
