    },
    {
      "TalkCharacters": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297
        }
      ],
      "WindowDisplayName": "Mizuki",
      "Body": "Well, all I was thinking about was 'Let's make a cute design!'~. I figured it probably couldn't actually be brought to life.",
